              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "UNFLD"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The  dependence  of  the  photoproton   cross",
                " section  on  photon  energy  over 40 - 105 MeV range",
                " assumed to be smooth was obtained  by  an  iterative",
                " procedure  from  the  present data.  The O-16(g,p-0)",
                " cross section then was obtained  from  a  particular",
                " proton  yield  spectrum  at  any  photon energy in a",
                " range corresponding to the top 5 MeV  of  the  yield",
                " spectrum   (the   residual   nucleus  N-15  has  the",
                " relatively large gap of more than 5 MeV between  its",
                " ground  state  and  first  excited  state and so all",
                " protons within about 5 MeV of the  endpoint  of  the",
                " proton  yield  spectrum  correspond to population of",
                " the ground state of N-15)."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "EN-SEC": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "E-LVL",
                "particle": "7-N-15"
              },
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ERR-ANALYS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-S",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The errors are due to statistics."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-1",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The systematic error was estimated to be about",
                " 11%."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The O-16(g,p-0)   reaction   has   been  investigated",
                " between photon energies Eg = 40 and 105 MeV using  a",
                " bremsstrahlung   beam,  full  angular  distributions",
                " being obtained at Eg = 60, 80, and 100 MeV."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "In accordance  to  note  added  in  proof  after  the",
                " publication all cross section  data  were  increased",
                " (by a compiler) by 6%  in connection with the effect",
                " of large electron energy losses in the gold radiator",
                " which previously have been neglected."
              ]
            }
          ],
